{start_of_verse: S1:}
[F]Tvoyi ochen'ka hnedy, tvoy i [C]usta solodky, ty miy anhel [Dm]kotryy khoronyt' mi sny. 
[F]Moye serdtse dam tobi, do svita[C] to rozpovim, zhe ty moya rybko[Dm] a ya iba tviy. 
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus: R1:}
[F]Zvyzdy svytyat' pre tebe, misyats'[C] svytyt' pre tebe, ta i sontse svytyt'[Dm] iba pre tebe! 
[F]I ya dykham pre tebe, uzh to [C]inche nebude, moye serdtse mi bye[Dm] iba pre tebe! 
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_grid: M1:}
| F | C | Dm | B |
| F | C | Dm | B |
{end_of_grid}

{start_of_verse: S2:}
[D]Krasny khvil'i za nami, koly [A]hvizdy padali, v tod'ik zme sya [Bm]lyubov moya spoznali . 
[D]Pershy bochky na lavtsi, pershy [A]bochky dalas' mi, a ya znav zhe uzh [Bm]yes' moya a ya tviy.
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus: R2:}
[D]Zvyzdy svytyat' pre tebe, misyats'[A] svytyt' pre tebe, ta i sontse svytyt'[Bm] iba pre tebe! 
[D]I ya dykham pre tebe, uzh to[A] inche nebude, moye serdtse mi[Bm] bye iba pre tebe! 
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_grid: M2:}
| D | A | Bm | G |
| D | A | Bm | G |
{end_of_grid}

