[F]Zvyzdy svytyat' pre tebe, misyats'[C] svytyt' pre tebe, ta i sontse svytyt'[Dm] iba pre tebe! 
[F]I ya dykham pre tebe, uzh[C] to inche nebude, moye serdtse mi [Dm]bye iba pre tebe!
[F]Zvyzdy svytyat' pre tebe, misyats'[C] svytyt' pre tebe, ta i sontse svytyt'[Dm] iba pre tebe! 
